## Acknowledgments

MD-Chat builds heavily on the work of:
- The Matrix.org Foundation and Element team (Synapse, Element X)
- The Signal Foundation (libsignal, Sealed Sender, PQXDH)
- The OpenMLS project (MLS RFC 9420 implementation)
- The LiveKit team (voice/video infrastructure)
- The Cronberry AI engine (Mega Promoting internal product, licensed for use)

We are grateful for the broader EU sovereign tech community: NLnet, Sovereign Tech Fund Germany, Prototype Fund, the FOSDEM organizing team, and the many activists, researchers, and policymakers fighting for end-to-end encryption and digital sovereignty in Europe.

